text: Harvey Birdman, Attorney at Law is an Adult Swim program that stars Birdman who started out as a super hero on the Hanna-Barbera program Birdman and the Galaxy Trio and is now a lawyer for Sebben Sebben. Several villains from that show return on this show and also brings back characters like Phil, Peanut, and Avenger. ==Cast== * Stephen Colbert as Phil and Reducto * Gary Cole as Harvey Birdman * John Michael Higgins as Mind Taker and Zardo * Peter Macnicol as X * Thomas Allen as Peanut Category:Adult Swim Category:English-language television programs
title: Harvey Birdman, Attorney at Law
